                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                            </head>
                            <p>For the position of the United States regarding the proposal of the
                                Secretary-General for the establishment of a United Nations security
                                guard, with reference to consideration of the matter by the General
                                Assembly at the second part of its third regular session in April
                                1949, see editorial note in <ref target="frus1948v01p1#pg_33">
                                    <hi rend="italic">Foreign Relations</hi>, 1948, volume I, page
                                    33</ref>.</p>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>